settings.title: About Us
settings.text:
Founded by two dog lovers who were tired of their dog being restless.

We were looking for a HEALTHY treat that will keep our dog busy for along-time while

we need to focus (or eat 😉).

We tried 100’s of different products, but none of them provided a real solution.

That’s why we created Freezbone; a unique refillable bone, that fills up with real food.

Keeps the house clean, and super-easy to use, Freezbone will keep your dog occupied for hours. 

As dog lovers, we believe your fur baby deserves the best quality food that keeps them healthy and happy for a long time.

Dan & Ariel

settings.title: Our mission
settings.content:
To provide dog owners peace of mind with our healthy refillable
meats and unique refillable bone.

settings.title: What is FreezBone made out of?
settings.subtitle: FreezBones are made using 100% natural rubber. The material is biodegradable and non-toxic so you can feel good about giving your pet these refillable bone treats!

settings.title: What are the refills made out of?
settings.subtitle:
Our treat refills are made from 100% real meat!

Beef

Beef, Beef liver, Chicken Liver, Water, Starch, Xanthan Gum, Tea Polyphenols, Carrageenan, Vitamin A, Vitamin B2, Niacin, Vitamin D3,
Isomaltooligosaccharide, D-Pantothenic Acid, D-Sodium Erythorbate

Duck

Duck, Chicken Liver, Water, Starch, Xanthan Gum, Tea Polyphenols, Carrageenan, Vitamin A, Vitamin B2, Niacin, Vitamin D3, Isomaltooligosaccharide, D-Pantothenic Acid, D-Sodium Erythorbate

Chicken

Chicken, Chicken Liver, Water, Starch, Xanthan Gum, Tea Polyphenols, Carrageenan,
Vitamin A, Vitamin B2, Niacin, Vitamin D3, Isomaltooligosaccharide, D-Pantothenic Acid, D-Sodium Erythorbate

 

Liver

Chicken Liver, Water, Starch, Xanthan Gum, Tea Polyphenols, Carrageenan, Vitamin A, Vitamin B2, Niacin, Vitamin D3, Isomaltooligosaccharide, D-Pantothenic Acid, D-Sodium Erythorbate

settings.title: Which FreezBone size is right for my dog?
settings.subtitle: FreezBones are intended for supplemental feeding. This product may be fed daily along with a complete and balanced dog food diet. Feed up to 1 pouch per day for an average-sized adult dog

settings.title: Is FreezBone dishwasher safe?
settings.subtitle: Yes, FreezBone is dishwasher-safe. Just toss it In the dishwasher and it is ready for its next use!

settings.title: Is the Freezbone works well with tough chewers?
settings.subtitle: While it is true that some strong chewers have been able to utilize the Freezbone without causing damage, it is still more suitable and recommended for dogs who are considered moderate chewers.

settings.title: Who Freezbone is most recommended for?
settings.subtitle: If you are in need of some "me time" and want to ensure that your furry companion isn't driving you up the wall, the Freezbone is the perfect solution for you. This versatile toy is highly recommended for dogs who require mental stimulation, relaxation, and enrichment. With the Freezbone, you can relax and enjoy some peace of mind knowing that your dog is happy and entertained.

settings.title: How do I make a purchase?
settings.subtitle:
1. To place an order, make sure you are logged in to your Freezbone account or create a new account. At checkout, you can also choose to place an order as a guest if you prefer not to create an account.

2. Click “Shop now” to see our products. Click on a product to see more details.

3. To add the product to your cart, click on the orange button that says “Add to Cart.”

4. After you add something to your cart, you can keep shopping or check out. To check out, click on the cart button on the upper right of your screen.

5. On the checkout page, add or select your shipping address. At this time, we only ship within the contiguous U.S.

6. Select your payment method. Before you place your order, review the items in your cart.

7. Any discounts or promotions will be reflected in your Order Total. When you’re ready, click the button that says “Place Order.” We’ll send you an email confirming your order.

settings.title: I received a promotion code. How do I apply it?
settings.subtitle: Applying a promotion code is simple! At Checkout, simply type the code into the box that says “Coupon Code.” Then, click the button that says “Apply.” All promotion codes can only be used once. Check Freezbone’s terms and conditions found on the email or mailer you received.

settings.title: When will my payment method be charged?
settings.subtitle: Your payment method will be charged automatically on the date the order is shipped. As soon as you place your order, you may see a pending charge for the total amount of the order. The pending charge will disappear 24 to 48 hours after your order ships. There's no need to call or update anything online.

settings.title: Why is my credit card not working?
settings.subtitle: If you’re having trouble with your credit card, make sure the billing address matches the address on file with your credit card and/or bank. Enter the name and credit card number exactly the way you see it on the card. Before you place your order, add the CVV, a 3-digit code found on the back of your card.

settings.title: What forms of payment do you accept?
settings.subtitle: We accept Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover, Apple Pay, Shop Pay, Affirm.

settings.title: What is the status of my order?
settings.subtitle:
Login at the top right-hand side of our site to track your order. Please Note: Order status & tracking information is not always updated in real-time, so please contact us in urgent situations.

You’ll receive an email to let you know we received your order. When your order ships, we’ll send another email with tracking information.

settings.title: How do I cancel or change my order?
settings.subtitle:
To cancel a Freezbone order before it shipped, please contact us with your order number ASAP at team@freezbone.com. Every effort will be made to accommodate the cancellation of your order as long as it has not yet been shipped.
Please note: if the item has been
shipped, the order cannot be canceled. In this case, you can request to return the item for a refund (minus shipping costs).

settings.title: How long does it take to get my order?
settings.subtitle: Most customers can expect to receive their food and supplies within 2 to 8 business days.

settings.title: Where are your products shipped from?
settings.subtitle: We currently ship from our warehouse in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.

settings.title: How much is shipping?
settings.subtitle:
Orders above $55 will ship FREE with USPS or UPS Ground - insurance included!

Orders under $29 will ship USPS at a 9 flat rate with insurance included!

settings.title: Who will be delivering my order?
settings.subtitle: We ship with both USPS and UPS.

settings.title: Do I need to be there to sign for it?
settings.subtitle: Nope! If you're not home, the driver will leave your package at the door, inside your mailbox, or with your doorman.

settings.title: Do you ship to P.O. boxes, APO/FPO addresses, or international addresses?
settings.subtitle: No – at this time we are unable to ship to P.O. boxes, APO/FPO addresses, and international addresses. We currently only ship within the contiguous US.

settings.title: What happens if my package gets lost?
settings.subtitle: All items purchased from Freezbone.com are made pursuant to a shipment contract, meaning that the risk of loss and title for such tems passes to you upon our delivery to the carrier. If your order is lost, please contact us at team@freezbone.com and we will do our best to help you locate it.

settings.title: How do I request a return or replacement?
settings.subtitle:
Our return policy is simple and worry-free: If you're not 100% unconditionally satisfied with your pet supplies, you can return them within 14 days of purchase. Products must be returned in original packaging without any missing tags or stickers. If you return treat fillers, they must be seal, never opened, just like your pup received it.

To start a return please go to our return center here

settings.title: What is the status of my refund?
settings.subtitle:
Depending on your banking institution, your refund will be credited back to your original payment method(s) in 3 to 5
business days.

settings.title: What if my dog doesn’t like it?
settings.subtitle: You can reach one of our devoted customer service reps at 33-272-6080 (SMS only) anytime between 9 AM to 5 PM EST. You can also email team@freezbone.com and we'll get back to you ASAP.

settings.title: What are your customer service hours?
settings.subtitle: We're available Monday to Friday, 9 AM -5 PM EST.

settings.title: How can I find out when an item is back in stock?
settings.subtitle:
When an item is out of stock, you can sign up to be notified when it’s available again. Go to the item page, enter your email address, and Click “Notify Me” to sign up. We’ll send one email notification for each item that’s back in stock.

NOTE: Signing up for notifications doesn’t reserve or guarantee item availability.

settings.title: Is there a minimum purchase amount for my order?
settings.subtitle: No, there is no minimum purchase required. You may purchase as many items as you need.

settings.title: What's your Privacy Policy?
settings.subtitle: Privacy is very important to us. Read our Privacy Policy for more details.
